  "keyFeatures": [
    "Generate 40+ native Apple target types (Widgets, App Clips, Watch Apps, Extensions)",
    "Continuous Native Generation - keep target source outside /ios directory",
    "CLI tool for scaffolding targets with templates",
    "Shared data between app and targets via App Groups",
    "Automatic entitlements and code signing configuration",
    "Support for Live Activities, Control Widgets, and WidgetKit",
    "Xcode project manipulation via @bacons/xcode",
    "CocoaPods integration for target customization"
